The Eagle Square in Abuja, venue of the All Progressives Congress (APC) national convention scheduled for Saturday, is currently a hive of activity. The venue has been adorned with different designs as well as posters and banners. The APC had earlier announced that all routes to the Eagle Square would be closed during the period of the convention. See pictures of the venue below. <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-679239" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="397" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-300x199.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-679245" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="397" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3.jpg 600w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3-300x199.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3-24x16.jpg 24w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3-36x24.jpg 36w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-3-48x32.jpg 48w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-679248" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-4.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="397" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/APC-convention-4.jpg 600w